[I] A simple cross-platform network library

[T] SDL_net is a network library that is used with the SDL library, and
[T] almost as portable. It allows a programmer to use network functionality
[T] without having to code different things for different platforms. It
[T] also simplyfies the handling of network connections and data transfer.

[U] https://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_net/

